title: OCE Youtubers
body:
So recently Youtube has been doing a few things regarding subscribers and whatnot, and as most should know, they have started unsubbing people from channels, i have experienced this myself (specifically with Yasei) and after having gone through my whole list i have noticed that i don't believe i have any of the OCE youtubers for league anymore.

So i'm making this post, to ask for you guys to just leave your links for these in the comments so i can resub to you guys again, you guys all deserve the subs, and youtube taking them away isn't what should be happening.

replies.body: Here's one of the coolest OCE youtubers: [KAYJAYBARACKUS](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqK0gqlifB33l_ydSYAaxKQ)

There are OCE LoL Youtubers?

I thought Brofesco was the only one and we kicked him out to the Poms.
